"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-26-jaaa-mourns-passing-double-olympian-george-rhoden\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"KINGSTON, Jamaica - Following the passing of double Olympic gold medallist George Rhoden, the Jamaica Athletics Administrative Association (JAAA) has honoured the veteran athlete, calling him \\\"one of the building blocks of our sport in Jamaica.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 17, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.99999999981776, \"rank\": 1.803139300025406e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 88, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Rhoden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"George Rhoden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Rhoden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Rhoden\"}, {\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamaica Athletics Administrative Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.99999999981776, \"rank\": 1.803139300025406e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement to the media on Monday, the JAAA expressed its grief saying it is \\\"in mourning as we learn of the passing of double Olympic gold medallist George Rhoden.\\\"\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 290, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JAAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Rhoden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"George Rhoden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Rhoden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Rhoden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"George Rhoden was one of the building blocks of our sport in Jamaica.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Rhoden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"George Rhoden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Rhoden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Rhoden\"}, {\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.99999999981776, \"rank\": 1.803139300025406e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He demonstrated true grit and determination in every single one of his races and was a dependable team member,\\\" said Garth Gayle, President of the JAAA.\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"score\": 0.9992282962062494, \"rank\": 0.0007573262243624073, \"text\": \"Gayle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\"}, {\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JAAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He would grind out every event, giving everything for his team and his country.\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His performances in 1952 will always be remembered as they laid the groundwork for the strong track and field nation we are today.\\\"\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rhoden, who won the 400m and was a member of the Golden Quartet that won the 4x400m at the Helsinki Olympics in 1952, passed away in the United States over the weekend.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 993, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8762856554223528, \"rank\": 0.14013095153692023, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": []}]}"